profiles.name: Lennise Germany
profiles.summary:
Founder/CEO at Livy O's · Lennise Germany is the CEO of Livy O’s Culinary Service Group. From humble beginnings selling meals from the trunk the family car in 2014, under Lennise's leadership Livy O's has thrived to servicing over 2000 meals per day for charter schools & rehabilitation facilities, become a preferred vendor for the USDA, performs wedding & banquet catering, and was one of 16 caterers to perform at the 2021 NFL Super Bowl. 

As one of the Bay Area’s most sought after caterers, Livy O’s, is not slowing down! As a chef, Lennise is routinely seen on ABC, NBC, and Fox television stations performing cooking demonstrations. As a CEO, Lennise serves as a board member of the South Tampa Chamber and a committee chair for the Minority Enterprise Program at the Tampa Bay Chamber of Commerce.
